data.description: Welcome to your new family home in the heart of Colesburg, Iowa! Situated in a peaceful and family-friendly neighborhood, this charming residence offers a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for creating lasting memories. With its convenient location and desirable features, this home is sure to attract buyers from all walks of life. From the inviting front porch to the spacious kitchen and lovely outdoor spaces, this property has everything a family needs to thrive. The front porch is adorned with large windows, flooding the entryway with natural light and providing a warm welcome to all visitors. The heart of the home is the large kitchen, which boasts an abundance of cabinets, offering ample storage space for all your culinary needs. This kitchen is perfect for hosting family gatherings and preparing delicious meals. The main floor features a bedroom, a bath, and a laundry, providing the convenience of single-level living. This setup is ideal for those who prefer to have essential amenities easily accessible. The dining room, adjacent to the kitchen, seamlessly flows into the spacious living room, creating an open and welcoming environment. This setup allows for effortless entertaining and quality family time. Upstairs, you'll find two cozy bedrooms, providing plenty of private space for family members or guests. Each room offers comfort, natural light, and the potential for customization to suit your individual needs. The lower level presents endless possibilities. Whether you envision a home office, a playroom, a media center, or a home gym, this space can be transformed to meet your family's unique requirements. Every man's dream, the oversize heated garage provides ample space for parking vehicles, storing outdoor equipment, and pursuing hobbies. It ensures year-round comfort and convenience for the whole family. In addition to the garage, an extra 12x24 shed offers more storage space or can be repurposed to suit your needs, whether it be a workshop, a studio, or a gardening shed. The exterior features a private patio adorned with a charming pergola, offering a delightful space for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. Enjoy the well-maintained green space, apple tree, and fragrant lilac bush, providing a serene and tranquil ambiance. This property is situated in a family-friendly community, with easy access to local amenities. Enjoy the peaceful small-town atmosphere while being within reach of larger cities for additional shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss this opportunity to own a warm, cozy, and family-friendly home in beautiful Colesburg, IA. Schedule a showing today and make this property your own!
